<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4d3e1a01-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s21751"><num value="21751">§ 21751.</num><heading> Model power of attorney legislation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Attorney General shall publish model power of attorney legislation for the purpose of preventing elder abuse.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4d3e1a02-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/70/tV/s504">Pub. L. 115–70, title V, § 504</ref>, <date date="2017-10-18">Oct. 18, 2017</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/131/1217">131 Stat. 1217</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
